ssh ubuntu@dev.thedoo.io	---------> Connect to dev server
deploy				----------> show all deployed microservices

==> select option for which microservice you have done changes and want to create new build & deploy again.

kc get po			----------> show all running pods(containers)
kc logs -f <pod_name>		----------> show current logs
kc get svc			----------> show services info along with ports on which it is running.
